data.description: Welcome to 2411 Nikki Drive, nestled within the serene Nikki Lakes Subdivision in Nesbit. This custom built, rustic country home boasts a spacious 3021 square feet of living space set upon a generous 1.51-acre lot, providing ample room for comfortable living and outdoor enjoyment. The upgraded windows provide for energy efficiency and sound.  The property features an occasional stream, granting water catchment privileges for irrigation by gardeners.  As you approach the home, you'll be greeted by a charming covered front porch adorned with wood bead board and a ceiling fan, perfect for relaxing evenings. Step inside to discover three bedrooms and three full bathrooms, including a large master bedroom featuring not one, but two walk-in closets and a luxurious walk-through shower with four shower heads. The gourmet kitchen showcases a large walk-in pantry, ideal for culinary enthusiasts. Upstairs, a landing area, bonus/game room with walk out balcony.  Indulge in relaxation within the soaker tub or retreat to the garden nursey.  The three-car garage provides ample storage and workspace, featuring two workbenches, a sink. Outside, a tranquil pond with a lighted fountain awaits, stocked with catfish, brim, and carp fish for the angler's delight. Additionally, discover a 10 x 10 storage area conveniently located under the balcony, ideal for stowing seasonal items. The first part of the attic serves as a greenhouse seedling nursery, providing a perfect space for nurturing plants. Special ground material under the swing set ensures safety and enjoyment for all ages. Experience luxurious living and peaceful surroundings at 2411 Nikki Drive—a place to call home.
